The operating principle of the BSNG is based on the coupling of contact electrification and electrostatic induction. The conduction mechanism for electricity transport is attributed to the Maxwell’s displacement current36, which can be defined as:1JD=∂D∂t=ε0∂E∂t+∂P∂t,\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
